name: Kraken
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: release the kraken
Developer Terms of Use
des: You never know what will happen if you release the kraken. But please don't taunt it or ask it to do the dishes because it has so many tentacles. It may seem that not much happens when you release the kraken. But often that's because its in another dimension or timeline or another part of the place where you're located. After releasing the kraken please cover all jars of peanut butter, place small children on high stools and don't let the kraken have any whiteboard markers.
